"normales FTP"
========:==:=====
in /etc/proftod. conf anpassen:
ServerName "ftp.proftpd. dmz"
Umask 002
002
in
/etc/proftpd/conf.d site. conf anlegen:
nano site.conf
DefaultRoot
Authorder
AuthuserFile/etc/proftpd/ftpd.passwd
AuthPAM off
RequireValidshell off
mod auth file.c
ftpd.passwd erzeugen: gid 1002
wwwadmin, uid 33
= www-data
cd /etc/proftpa
ftpasswd -passwd -name ftpuser -gid 1002 -uid 33
-home /www/www.smartlearn.dmz
-shell /bin/false
systemctl restart proftpd. service
testen!
2.
mod sftpd
